{"tid":134012,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發] 長毛宣布不參選特首","createTime":"2017-02-25T06:39:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-25T14:53:13.000Z","uid":52546,"like":6,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2d55f624f39f1ad03adfe5488eca35c36b09f6bc","tid":134012,"uid":52546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T06:39:25.000Z","msg":"早前聲稱收集到3.8萬個公民提名，會參選特首的社民連立法會議員梁國雄，今日宣佈在2星期內，於網上及街頭一共收到2,0234個公民提名，未達目標，宣佈不會參選特首，結束收集公民提名。梁國雄表示，感謝市民支持，指提名的人需留下聯絡方法及身份證號碼，對他的信任是非常大。<br />\n<br />\n長毛指坊間有意見認為，有曾俊華參選便足夠，批評長毛參選是鎅票，團隊爭取提名時受到責備，他感謝團隊在壓力下，仍然到街頭為他爭取公民提名。"},{"pid":"ef6a367936f442dd77bde21636392eeee2b8b79d","tid":134012,"uid":28397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T06:44:32.000Z","msg":"鎅票失敗 收工 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93a1bea95199f220dddfe98e716db72ed275bfa7","tid":134012,"uid":42820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T06:45:35.000Z","msg":"架係自己丟"},{"pid":"4d331789a40a0132fa34d1daff0ae854ff377c70","tid":134012,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T06:46:25.000Z","msg":"我都唔知你做乜狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7d18538b53f2783c530a09aae1f288c0fde0eb2","tid":134012,"uid":24781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T06:47:16.000Z","msg":"又要威又要戴頭盔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"666feeea7767ad908c3cb44e6b4e48f6b1650bb7","tid":134012,"uid":57237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T06:48:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2111a70f2616d065ff5ef2e74fc77027dff2cfd5","tid":134012,"uid":8954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T06:48:18.000Z","msg":"wa 又聯絡電話又